# 5 Non-Negotiable Strategic Constraints

이미 `main.mdc` 영역 명시. 추가 detail:

## Pivot Threshold (vault 56 §2 amended by vault 61 v2)

- **8-week (2026-08-07)** < 10 user → **Pivot 0 — Acquisition Iterate** (positioning maintain + channel 5+ test)
- **16-week (2026-10-02)** still < 10 user → **Pivot 1 — Self-Discovery**
- **24-week (2026-11-27)** still < 10 user → ★ HARD SUNSET 강제 trigger ★

Pivot direction priority: Acquisition Iterate 1st → Self-Discovery 2nd → Holistic 3rd → 영문 4th → Sub-cluster swap 5th → B2B 6th

## Cost Economics (vault 62 §1 Q4.2 amended)

V1 realistic Total Claude cost: ~**$427-447/mo** (Tier 0 영역 30% utilization 가정, Sonnet default):
- Tier 0: 1.5 msg/day × 100 user × Sonnet = $94.5/mo
- Tier 1: 6 msg/day × 30 user × Sonnet = $113/mo
- Tier 2 Pro: 30 msg/day × 10 user × Sonnet = $189/mo
- Layer 1 Opus daily: $30-50/mo

V1 revenue: Tier 2 10 user × $19 = $190/mo → **-$237-257/mo gross margin** (PIVOT trigger acceptable burn per vault 56 §2).

V1.5 mitigation: Layer 2 + Haiku routing enable 영역 60-80% cost reduction → break-even early.

**CTO escalate threshold**: actual cost 영역 vault 62 §1 Q4.2 ±20% deviation 시 CEO ping.

## Per-tier chat quota (vault 62 §1 Q3 lock-in)

- Tier 0 anonymous: 5 msg/day, 100 msg/month
- Tier 1 free signup: 20 msg/day, 400 msg/month
- Tier 2 Pro: 100 msg/day, 2000 msg/month
- Tier 3 Premium: V1 defer (unlimited fallback)

PostHog events: `chat_quota_hit` (80%/100% threshold) + `chat_quota_blocked` (100% blocked count)

